---
import sectionBg from '@/assets/images/960c78e88976.jpg';
import posterImg from '@/assets/images/4e11a1312c89.jpg';
---

<section class="media-bg section hfk-s4-results" style="--scrim-strength:0.55">
  <img class="media-bg__img media-bg__img--blur" src={sectionBg.src} alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1440" height="800" />
  <span class="media-bg__scrim media-bg__scrim--b"></span>

  <div class="media-bg__inner container on-media">
    <div class="hfk-s4__inner">

      <h2 class="hfk-s4__heading">Real Results</h2>

      <p class="hfk-s4__body">
        HydraFacial™ Keravive™ is an excellent complement to hair restoration treatments such as PRP, microneedling, or medication. By creating a healthy scalp environment, it maximizes the effectiveness of all other treatments you may be undergoing.
      </p>

      <p class="hfk-s4__body">
        Clinical studies show that 97% of patients reported an improvement in scalp health after three treatments, with 93% reporting improvement in hair fullness and 79% reporting reduction in hair shedding.
      </p>

      <p class="hfk-s4__body">
        Watch one of our actual clients experience their comfortable and rejuvenating Keravive treatment.
      </p>

      <div class="hfk-s4__video-wrap">
        <video
          class="hfk-s4__video"
          data-lazy-video
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          preload="none"
          poster={posterImg.src}
          width="1280"
          height="720"
        >
          <source data-src="/videos/wix/2baa5c_1059a76a02f24c61bdde516852248949.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          <track kind="descriptions" />
        </video>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hfk-s4-results {
    min-height: 600px;
  }

  .hfk-s4__inner {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hfk-s4__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .hfk-s4__body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hfk-s4__video-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 800px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hfk-s4__video {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hfk-s4-results {
      min-height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
